---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Technology - intelio">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal mb-4 sm:mb-6">Technology</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-6 sm:mb-8">Built to support real businesses, not demos.</p>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>Technology only creates value when it aligns with how a business actually operates.</p>
        <p>At intelio, technology is not the product — it's the infrastructure that makes execution reliable, scalable, and visible.</p>
        <p>We design, integrate, and operate systems that sit underneath revenue, operations, finance, and decision-making — applying AI and automation only where it creates real leverage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Our Philosophy (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-3 sm:mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-6 sm:mb-8">Technology should disappear into the business.</p>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">Most organizations don't fail because they lack tools. They fail because tools are fragmented, poorly integrated, or misaligned with how work actually happens.</p>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our approach is simple:</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Business intent first</p>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Systems second</p>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Technology last</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">We do not chase trends, ship novelty, or deploy AI for optics. Every system we build must support execution, reduce friction, or improve decision quality.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: The Intelio Operating Layers (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-3 sm:mb-4">The Intelio Operating Layers</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-400 mb-12 sm:mb-16">Rather than selling tools, we architect operating layers that work together.</p>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION: Layer 1 (Light) -->
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-12 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Core Business Systems</h3>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-6">These are the systems your teams touch every day.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>CRM and revenue systems</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Operations and workflow management</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Scheduling, dispatch, and execution tooling</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Accounting, billing, and financial control</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">We design these systems around actual workflows, not software defaults.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION: Layer 2 (Dark) -->
      <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Automation & Integration Layer</h3>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-6">This is where fragmentation disappears.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Workflow orchestration across tools</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Event-driven automation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Data synchronization and validation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Notifications, alerts, and handoffs</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Audit and compliance logging</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">This layer ensures information moves cleanly across the organization — without manual effort.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION: Layer 3 (Light) -->
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-12 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Intelligence & AI Layer</h3>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-6">AI is applied selectively, not universally.</p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">We deploy intelligence where it meaningfully improves outcomes, such as:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Lead prioritization and routing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Forecasting and scenario modeling</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Cost and margin anomaly detection</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Document analysis and abstraction</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Decision support and summarization</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">AI is embedded into workflows — not bolted on as a separate experience.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION: Layer 4 (Dark) -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Visibility & Decision Layer</h3>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-6">Executives need clarity, not dashboards for dashboards' sake.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Real-time performance visibility</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>KPI standardization across departments</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Drill-down from summary to transaction</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Early warning signals for risk and variance</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">This layer turns data into decisions — not reports.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Platforms We Standardize On (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">Platforms We Standardize On</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">We work with proven, enterprise-grade platforms to ensure durability, security, and scalability.</p>
      
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Enterprise Foundations</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Microsoft</h4>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">Identity, automation, data, AI, and enterprise infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Google</h4>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">Workspace, analytics, search, and local presence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic text-center mb-12">These platforms form the backbone of many systems we deploy.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Business Systems & Tooling</h3>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">Depending on the organization, systems may include:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>CRM and revenue platforms</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Accounting and financial systems</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Operations and scheduling tools</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Data warehouses and reporting layers</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Automation and integration frameworks</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">We select tools based on fit, maturity, and operational reliability, not hype.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Configured, Not Fragile (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">Configured, Not Fragile</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">intelio configures proven systems to your business.</p>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">We do not:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Build fragile one-off stacks</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Reinvent commodity software</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Experiment on production businesses</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Customization happens through architecture, integration, and workflow design, not brittle code.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Custom & Advanced Technology Projects (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">Custom & Advanced Technology Projects</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">In select cases, off-the-shelf tools are not sufficient.</p>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">For organizations operating at scale or complexity, we undertake custom system design and advanced AI-enabled projects, including:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Internal platforms and proprietary tooling</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Specialized data and decision workflows</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Cross-department intelligence systems</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Advanced automation and orchestration</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>AI-driven analysis and decision support</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">These engagements are:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Selective</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Independently scoped</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Designed for long-term operation</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">Custom work is not the default — it is reserved for situations where standard systems break down.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Security, Governance, and Reliability (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-3 sm:mb-4">Security, Governance, and Reliability</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-6 sm:mb-8">Systems must be trusted to be used.</p>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">We design with:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Role-based access control</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Data governance and auditability</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Compliance awareness</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Production-grade reliability</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">Technology decisions are made with long-term ownership in mind.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What This Means for You (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What This Means for You</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">You are not locked into experimental tools</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Your systems evolve as the business evolves</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">AI enhances execution instead of distracting from it</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Technology supports leadership decisions — not the other way around</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: How This Connects to How We Work (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">How This Connects to How We Work</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">Technology is delivered through our engagement models:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Identify + Build + Maintain</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Identify + Build + Operate</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Selective Custom & Advanced Builds</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">Each ensures systems are not only built — but kept aligned to the business.</p>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/how-we-work" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black text-base sm:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors min-h-[56px]">
          Explore How We Work
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Closing (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-900 leading-relaxed mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        Technology should make your business easier to run, not harder to understand.<br>
        That's the standard intelio builds to.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-black text-white text-base sm:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors min-h-[56px]">
        Work with Intelio
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

